The paper focuses on face recognition using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of transfer learning and deep feature fusion also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves the use of linear SVMs for enhancing discrimination, which falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Finally, the paper also involves evaluation and comparison of performance, which falls under the cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-category.
